        {
            "id": 6438079,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 邁科(6831)大漲7.05%，報493.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>邁科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6831:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6831\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6831-TW</a>)30日12:04股價上漲32.5元，報493.5元，漲幅7.05%，成交901張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>邁科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6831:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6831\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6831-TW</a>)所屬產業為電腦及週邊設備業，主要業務為散熱模組。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌15.41%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.76%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,138 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-974 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-160 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-4 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6438079",
